# Google reCAPTCHA v2 SITE key (public — it is embedded in the page HTML).
# This static site hardcodes the value in index.html's data-sitekey, so this
# file is only documentation. The matching SECRET key is private and must be
# added in the Formspree form settings, never committed here.
VITE_RECAPTCHA_SITE_KEY=your-recaptcha-site-key
